            <title>[GROOVY-8686] STC: type inferencing for (a instanceof C &amp;&amp; a...) bleeds into enclosing scope</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-8686</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Expecting type checking error for the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
@groovy.transform.TypeChecked
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; m(&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; obj) {
  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; isA = (obj &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;instanceof&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; &amp;amp;&amp;amp; obj.equalsIgnoreCase(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;a&apos;&lt;/span&gt;))
  obj.toLowerCase() &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// should be STC error; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; above line is commented out, error shows
&lt;/span&gt;}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Same for &lt;tt&gt;@CompileStatic&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
